com.tsgrp.migration.cache

Interface IEagerCache<T,U>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The key mapping to a specified value.
    U - The value(s) held by the cache.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEagerCache, BasicStringToStringCache, StringToMapCache

    public interface IEagerCache<T,U>
    Interface for a cache which holds string-value pairs, can be generated via. a defined a method, and returns the value when requested. Actual implementations should specify the type parameters.
